## 13. MASTER PRE-CODING CHECKLIST (MANDATORY)

Copy into PR description or task close-out when applicable:

**Context**
- [ ] Domain profile(s) detected: ___
- [ ] Profile P0 invariants listed and enforced
- [ ] Scope calibrated (trivial / local / feature / architecture)

**Architecture & code**
- [ ] No cross-boundary imports; APIs/events only
- [ ] Transport thin; logic owns orchestration
- [ ] Typed contracts at boundaries; no raw dicts through layers
- [ ] Config via `settings` / env — no hardcoded secrets or URLs
- [ ] Async-safe: no blocking in async handlers
- [ ] No shared mutable module state

**Data & API**
- [ ] No N+1; indexes for hot queries
- [ ] Pagination on lists; idempotency on mutations
- [ ] Standard error shape; no internal leak
- [ ] Long work async (202 + job) not blocking HTTP

**Resilience & security**
- [ ] Timeouts + bounded retries + jitter on outbound calls
- [ ] Circuit breaker / fail-fast where dependency critical
- [ ] Parameterized queries; SSRF checks on URLs
- [ ] AuthZ on every object access; rate limits considered

**Observability & quality**
- [ ] Structured logs + correlation ID; no PII/secrets logged
- [ ] Health endpoints present
- [ ] Unit tests on behavior; clients mocked; failure paths covered
- [ ] Dependencies pinned; Dockerfile layer order sane

