## 14. ANTI-PATTERN → MITIGATION QUICK MAP

| Symptom in prod | Likely anti-pattern | First fix |
|---|---|---|
| Duplicate charges | Non-idempotent POST | Idempotency key + unique constraint |
| Random 500s under load | Blocking event loop | Async client or thread offload |
| Slow list API | N+1 or no pagination | Batch query + limit/cursor |
| OOM on export | Unbounded read | Stream/chunk |
| Cross-tenant data leak | Missing tenant filter | RLS + middleware guard |
| Agent runaway cost | Unbounded loop | max_iterations + budget kill |
| Stale UI after write | Replica lag read | Read primary or delay UX |
| Retry amplified outage | No jitter | Exponential backoff + cap |

